# URL Checker Service API Tests

### Create a new job
POST http://localhost:3000/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "urls": [
    "https://example.com",
    "https://google.com",
    "https://github.com",
    "https://nonexistent-domain-123456.com"
  ]
}

### Get all jobs
GET http://localhost:3000/api/jobs

### Get job details (replace :id with actual job ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/jobs/:id

### Cancel a job (replace :id with actual job ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/jobs/:id

### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health